snippet.title: Awaken - Astral blade | Official Trailer | Gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Awaken - Astral blade will make a brilliant appearance on Gamescom 2023. 
Join us at hall 10.2 - stand E040 to embark on a captivating adventure with AWAKEN - Astral Blade at Gamescom 2023. 

You could find this Metroidvania game at:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1716310/

Welcome to join our Channel and find out the story of Loretta.
Discord: 
https://discord.gg/ZWApKgrgdA
Twitter: 
https://twitter.com/AwakenBlade
